天</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上后，放弃了肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的新“diss 曲目”。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Father-John-Misty-and-Kendrick-Lamar.-CREDIT_-Harmony-Gerber_Getty-Images-and-Gary-Miller_WireImage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 在发布新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/father-john-misty-mahashmashana-review-3814237">《Mahashmashana》</a>的同一天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-brand-new-album-gnx-listen-in-full-3815187">意外发行了他的新专辑《GNX》</a>后，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/father-john-misty">约翰·米斯蒂 (John Misty) 神父</a>分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 的</a>一首 diss 歌曲。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/father-john-mi